http://citeseerx.ist.psu.edu/viewdoc/download?doi=10.1.1.330.6508&rep=rep1&type=pdf

Treats the normal case expressed in COI1987.
It is therefore more detailed since it is the only method treated.
In this paper, much more details are given on the correlation matrix.

Once again the data used are just numerical examples chosen by the author,
but in this case they explicitely prove the decision maker needs a lot knowledge concerning the experts.
